walk-with-god?lang=fra\"><small>GÉ</small> Marcher, marcher avec Dieu</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/walk-walk-with-god?lang=fra","text":"GÉ Marcher, marcher avec Dieu"}]},"note3b":{"id":"note3b","marker":"3b","pid":"117840154","context":"loi","text":"<p data-aid=\"117840207\" id=\"note3b_p1\"><small>HÉB</small> enseignement, doctrine. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/gospel?lang=fra\"><small>GÉ</small> Évangile</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/gospel?lang=fra","text":"GÉ Évangile"}]},"note4a":{"id":"note4a","marker":"4a","pid":"117840156","context":"juge","text":"<p data-aid=\"117840209\" id=\"note4a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/21.2-9?lang=fra#p2\">2 Né 21:2–9</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/21.2-9?lang=fra#p2","text":"2 Né 21:2–9"}]},"note5a":{"id":"note5a","marker":"5a","pid":"117840158","context":"égarés","text":"<p data-aid=\"117840211\" id=\"note5a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/28.14?lang=fra#p14\">2 Né 28:14</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.6?lang=fra#p6\">Mos 14:6</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.37?lang=fra#p37\">Al 5:37</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/28.14?lang=fra#p14","text":"2 Né 28:14"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.6?lang=fra#p6","text":"Mos 14:6"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.37?lang=fra#p37","text":"Al 5:37"}]},"note6a":{"id":"note6a","marker":"6a","pid":"117840160","context":"sont","text":"<p data-aid=\"117840213\" id=\"note6a_p1\"><small>CÀD</small> rempli, imprégné d’enseignements, de croyances étrangères. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/ps/106.35?lang=fra#p35\">Ps 106:35</a>.</p>","r